claim.claim-text:
An agricultural work vehicle comprising:
a radiator mounted on the vehicle chassis frame in front of the engine in the engine compartment;
an air cleaner support disposed in front of the radiator;
the vehicle chassis, the length of which extends forward in front of the air cleaner support;
a battery stored in the space created by the vehicle chassis frame extending forward in front of the air cleaner support; and
an engine control unit securely disposed above the battery inside an engine compartment space by means of a fixing bracket secured to a side of the air cleaner support.
